claims:
10. A method controlling telecommunications in a telecommunications system, said method comprising the steps of:
preparing an own node constituting the telecommunications system together with another node, the own node including a reception power decider, a control signal decider and a communication controller;
causing the reception power decider to determine a reception power value of a control signal received from the other node;
causing the control signal decider to decide, in accordance with the reception power value of the control signal determined by the reception power decider, whether or not the own node should communicate with the other node in relation to interference at the own node; and
causing the communication controller to control communication between the own node and the other node in accordance with a result of a decision made by the control signal decider.
